      "description": "The Hartford Equity Premium Income ETF (HEMI) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in large cap equity. The fund is an actively managed portfolio of large-cap US stocks aiming for income and capital appreciation. To generate yields, the fund utilizes a laddered call writing strategy on the SPDR S&P 500 ETF Trust (SPY) or on the S&P 500 Index. HEMI was launched on Dec 17, 2025 and is issued by The Hartford.",
